                        "What color packaging to use"
                    ],
                    correct: 1
                },
                {
                    question: "What does economics ask about actors?",
                    options: [
                        "Who should star in commercials",
                        "Who is organizing and controlling production and distribution",
                        "Who has the most money",
                        "Who works the hardest"
                    ],
                    correct: 1
                },
                {
                    question: "Why study economics for business students?",
